      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="プレイしたゲーム"><a href="#プレイしたゲーム" class="headerlink" title="プレイしたゲーム"></a>プレイしたゲーム</h2><ul><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3250010/_/">霜夜ゆく</a><ul><li>ほぼ全通り試し終えたので、多分クリアは行ける、そこまでやらんでも良かった気がするけど</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="リンク"><a href="#リンク" class="headerlink" title="リンク"></a>リンク</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.famitsu.com/article/202506/45495">終天教団</a><ul><li>気になるけど先にダンロンに手を付けるべきという説もある</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="雑記"><a href="#雑記" class="headerlink" title="雑記"></a>雑記</h2><p>サマーセール、あんまり買う気なかったのに気づいたら買っていた。</p><table><thead><tr><th>A Highland Song</th><th>Ascent DX</th><th>Birth</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1240060/A_Highland_Song/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240060/header.jpg?t=1745516629"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3384890/Ascent_DX/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384890/header.jpg?t=1748894723"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1889040/Birth/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/header.jpg?t=1739362118"></a></td></tr><tr><td>音楽が良いらしい</td><td>ミニマルなメトロイドヴァニア枠</td><td>変なゲームっぽい</td></tr><tr><td>Chroma Zero</td><td>ENA: Dream BBQ</td><td>Footgun: Underground</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3121470/Chroma_Zero/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121470/header.jpg?t=1749586994"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2134320/ENA_Dream_BBQ/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134320/header.jpg?t=1745442442"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2206240/Footgun_Underground/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206240/header.jpg?t=1747385033"></a></td></tr><tr><td>良いパズルらしい</td><td>リリースを待っていた変なゲーム</td><td>サッカーローグライクアクション、気になる</td></tr><tr><td>Freedom Maker</td><td>Gestalt: Steam &amp; Cinder</td><td>Ginger</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3356540/Freedom_Maker/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356540/header.jpg?t=1736852638"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1231990/Gestalt_Steam__Cinder/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231990/header.jpg?t=1729786474"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3418910/Ginger/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3418910/header.jpg?t=1743253507"></a></td></tr><tr><td>妙なゲーム性してそう</td><td>中規模程度のメトロイドヴァニア枠</td><td>どうせゲームじゃないんだろうなの気持ち</td></tr><tr><td>Lingo</td><td>Little Witch Nobeta</td><td>Many Nights a Whisper</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1814170/Lingo/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814170/header.jpg?t=1729365387"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1049890/Little_Witch_Nobeta/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1049890/header.jpg?t=1740912949"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3541130/Many_Nights_a_Whisper/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541130/4af9e60c962faf3e31e407dfafc8c5e1247daf84/header.jpg?t=1747845694"></a></td></tr><tr><td>言語パズルらしい</td><td>今更ノベタやる人になる</td><td>これも一つのOneshot</td></tr><tr><td>Moonbase Lambda</td><td>Moonscars</td><td>Only Sliding</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2636910/Moonbase_Lambda/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/header.jpg?t=1746616813"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1374970/Moonscars/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374970/header.jpg?t=1687296135"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3575260/Only_Sliding/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3575260/2cb5acb1eadcc8edca66c71c6a1016f6fdfd4f65/header.jpg?t=1745879489"></a></td></tr><tr><td>たまにホラーっぽいのもやる</td><td>暗めのメトロイドヴァニア枠</td><td>Recursedの作者さんらしい</td></tr><tr><td>Sisyphe’s Backspace</td><td>Slay the Alice</td><td>Teleport Master</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3615480/Sisyphes_Backspace/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615480/c83a703bb434375604ab373c80f42611a4aa33ba/header.jpg?t=1750565102"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3048760/Slay_the_Alice/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/header_japanese.jpg?t=1751015236"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3406610/Teleport_Master/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406610/header_japanese.jpg?t=1748592455"></a></td></tr><tr><td>バックスペースを使うゲームらしい</td><td>SlayのADV枠の方</td><td>ワンボタンゲー、好き</td></tr><tr><td>Tiny Dangerous Dungeons Remake</td><td>Voxelgram</td><td>シャンハイ サマー</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3179810/Tiny_Dangerous_Dungeons_Remake/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/header.jpg?t=1741277959"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1158470/Voxelgram/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158470/header.jpg?t=1745391119"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1323830/_/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323830/header_japanese.jpg?t=1710241941"></a></td></tr><tr><td>こういうアクションをたまにやりたくなる</td><td>Mega Mosaic枠</td><td>こういうシナリオ系、大体一つは買う</td></tr><tr><td>ドラゴンクエストXI　過ぎ去りし時を求めて S</td><td>ホーンティー</td><td>ライムの森で待つ</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1295510/XI__S/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1295510/header.jpg?t=1727228467"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2060790/_/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/header_japanese.jpg?t=1750079178"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2690110/_/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2690110/header_japanese.jpg?t=1751015168"></a></td></tr><tr><td>ドラクエ、IとIIしかやってないのはどうなんだということで</td><td>ビジュアル枠</td><td>不穏シナリオ枠</td></tr><tr><td>未解決事件は終わらせないといけないから</td><td>水たまりのスペクトル</td><td>片腕のザリガニ - one-armed crayfish</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2676840/_/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676840/header_japanese.jpg?t=1747299882"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3302900/_/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302900/header_japanese.jpg?t=1738116113"></a></td><td><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3509770/__onearmed_crayfish/"><img src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509770/header_japanese.jpg?t=1740064091"></a></td></tr><tr><td>そろそろ始めないといけない</td><td>シンプルなアクション</td><td>いつかやるので</td></tr></tbody></table><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/spoiler.css" type="text/css"><script src="/js/spoiler.js" type="text/javascript" async></script>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
